title: M. Watkinson - Crazy Diamond: Syd Barrett and Dawn of Pink Floyd
description: Crazy Diamond: Syd Barrett and the Dawn of Pink Floyd by Mike Watkinson and Pete Anderson 192 pages Publisher: Omnibus Press; Revised edition edition (17 Aug. 2006) Retail epub Syd Barrett was Pink Floyd's founder, singer, guitarist and principal composer, who left the group in 1968 amidst tales of acid-induced madness. Barrett's brief flash of erratic brilliance has is now the stuff of rock legend, and his post-Floyd recordings have become cult classics. Updated for 2006, this book draws on years on research to relate an epic rock tragedy. https://pirates-forum.org/Forum-Requests
